Events.Text: Maybe the AI Assistant can help? Say hello and ask if it can help you plan the party. [instruction 1 of 7]
Hello. My name is Ben. Myself and a friend named Angela want to organize a birthday party. We will have 7 people. Can you help?
Angela says: 'I think the Southside Venue is quite nice'. [instruction 2 of 7]

Scenario.UserTask: You (Ben) and your friend Angela want to organize a birthday party on Saturday. You expect 7 guests to come.
Scenario.WizardTask: Follow the flow charts and help the user. Note: If the user already knows a restaurant name, use 'restaurant reserve', otherwise use 'restaurant search'.
